      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presenting a meticulously maintained vehicle that balances performance with enduring value. This unit has undergone a comprehensive multi-point inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and aesthetic standards meet our rigorous criteria. Ideal for the discerning driver seeking a reliable, high-caliber driving experience without the premium of a showroom-new price point. Secure this exceptional value today.",
