    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape\u2014well-cared for and definitely ready for its next big adventure! It runs smoothly and has been super dependable for all my daily trips. If you\u2019re looking for a great car that\u2019s been treated right and still has plenty of life left, this is the one for you. Feel free to reach out, I\u2019d love to tell you more about it!",
      "price": 31500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
