      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 24
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride and I honestly think you\u2019re going to love it. It\u2019s been such a reliable companion for me and it\u2019s still in really solid shape, just waiting for its next adventure! It drives smoothly and has been well-cared for, making it perfect for someone who wants a dependable vehicle without the 'brand new' price tag. If you\u2019re looking for a great deal on a car that still has tons of life left in it, come take a look! I'm super easy to talk to, so feel free to reach out with any questions!",
      "price": 31500.0,
