    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 features the legendary S54 3.2L inline-six, delivering 333 hp through six individual throttle bodies and a crisp Getrag 6-speed manual transmission. The chassis remains taut with a factory-spec limited-slip differential and recently inspected subframe mounts. Maintenance is up to date, including a VANOS overhaul and valve adjustment, ensuring the high-revving valvetrain operates with mechanical precision. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, this driver-focused machine offers balanced weight distribution and communicative steering feedback. A well-sorted example ready for the apex.",
